            About the Library
          Heading link



 
Copy link







          The Circle Campus Reading Room in the Daley Library.
        


The Richard J. Daley Library collections cover the arts, humanities, sciences, social sciences, and engineering. Special Collections & University Archives houses rare books and printed materials, manuscript collections, and university archives, specializing in the history of Chicago.



      Who was Richard J. Daley?
    








